OL,5, Energy bills could fall further than   
OL,6, previously forecast later this year,   
OL,7, easing pressure on struggling          
OL,8, households, new projections suggest.   
OL,10,FLess generous government help means a  
OL,11,Ftypical household gas and electricity  
OL,12,Fbill is expected to rise from #2,500 a 
OL,13,Fyear to #3,000 a year in April.        
OL,15,FBut falling wholesale gas prices mean  
OL,16,Fannual bills could fall below this from
OL,17,FJuly, says finance firm Investec.      
OL,19,FIt predicts customers will be paying   
OL,20,F#2,478 a year from that point.         
